<paragraph blockId="1.[151,1437,1287,1565]" pageId="1" pageNumber="273">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,267,1287,1312]" pageId="1" pageNumber="273">Remarks.</emphasis>
The Zoology part of the Coquille voyage book series was printed in numerous fascicles (livraisons) over many years and in spite of the 
<number box="[500,556,1324,1348]" pageId="1" pageNumber="273" value="1830.0">1830</number>
date printed on the front page, the text of “Insecta” by Guérin-Méneville was printed only in 
<number box="[336,392,1360,1384]" pageId="1" pageNumber="273" value="1838.0">1838</number>
(
<bibRefCitation author="Cretella" box="[411,574,1359,1384]" pageId="1" pageNumber="273" refString="Cretella, M. (2010) The complete collation and dating of the section Zoologie of the Coquille voyage. Bollettino Malacologico, 46 (2), 83 - 103." type="journal article" year="2010">
Cretella 
<number box="[513,574,1360,1384]" pageId="1" pageNumber="273" value="2010.0">2010</number>
</bibRefCitation>
). However, the livraison No. 
<number box="[924,952,1360,1384]" pageId="1" pageNumber="273" value="19.0">19</number>
with plate 
<number box="[1090,1104,1360,1384]" pageId="1" pageNumber="273" value="2.0">2</number>
illustrating this species was published in 
<number box="[295,351,1396,1420]" pageId="1" pageNumber="273" value="1830.0">1830</number>
(
<bibRefCitation author="Cretella" box="[366,521,1396,1421]" pageId="1" pageNumber="273" refString="Cretella, M. (2010) The complete collation and dating of the section Zoologie of the Coquille voyage. Bollettino Malacologico, 46 (2), 83 - 103." type="journal article" year="2010">
Cretella 
<number box="[463,521,1396,1420]" pageId="1" pageNumber="273" value="2010.0">2010</number>
</bibRefCitation>
) validating the joint description of genus and species— 
<taxonomicName box="[1145,1304,1397,1420]" class="Insecta" family="Melyridae" genus="Laius" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="1" pageNumber="273" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="cyaneus">
<emphasis box="[1145,1304,1397,1420]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="273">Laius cyaneus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
